{"type": "article", "id": 34952, "title": "有人为库里做了专刊，以及，“可以住的书店”推出第二期 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-28T02:39:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1865, "name": "书店"}, {"id": 4586, "name": "黑色星期五"}, {"id": 24768, "name": "篮球场"}, {"id": 35253, "name": "球鞋杂志"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 14370, "name": "reebok"}, {"id": 35254, "name": "Digger"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161128091025ODYy6dnSab7oltji.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://qz.com/846415/black-friday-2016-report-shows-shoppers-broke-online-and-mobile-sales-records/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>今年黑五，移动端消费突破 12 亿美元</b></a> | 根据 Adobe 的网络销售报告称，今年黑五，网络销售达到了 33.4 亿美元，其中，移动端消费突破 12 亿美元。从感恩节至黑五的这个期间，整体网络销售达 52.7 亿美元。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.geekwire.com/2016/boutique-fashion-e-commerce-platform-garmentory-raises-2m-takes-larger-retailers/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>精品时尚电商 Garmentory 获 200 万美元融资 </b></a>| 创立于 2014 年的女性精品时尚电商 Garmentory 获得 200 万美元融资。作为一个网络电商，Garmentory 有超过 350 家供应商，这些供应商以世界各地的时尚精品店和独立设计师品牌为主，目前，Garmentory 的商品来自两千多个不同品牌和设计师。有消息称，该网站在今年和明年的销售额同比增幅达 500%，并将于明年进军男装领域。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>在 12 月 3 日 Nike 精选挑选的  12 Soles 系列正式发售之际，它邀请林子楠（Zinan Lam）、蔡嘉鳌（SINIC)、WHYYY 这三位艺术家，以<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/nike-12-soles-graffiti-shanghai\" rel=\"nofollow\">「中国 Sneaker 的足迹」</a>为主题，在上海嘉定体育中心的篮球场上打造了巨型涂鸦画作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281017014bzga6QWKpMqjoYr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101701SydWxGXU0mwKapN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101712PQAz6JFGWDHdoRlg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101712nFeByLsSVi9wd4fO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101712aqoAO9J2w8VxDpMs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101713x6ugCJLe7lyw9PTK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/reebok-aztec-collection-70\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reebok 发布全新的 Aztec 复刻系列</a>，在保留原有的轮廓的基础上，结合麂皮和尼龙打造鞋身，并发布了全新的配色。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101619NP7J4nokhlWsZ2IO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101619uoP8GQ4b3e6C7htN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101629Oj2deGIJHorvl6Fz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101636qPYsacfH0jE1A8Fn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101643VP0TL6Gyac2xQWAd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">可以住的书店<a href=\"http://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2016-11-25/book-and-bed-kyoto/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> BOOK AND BED TOKYO</a>，继 2015 年在池袋开业之后一直颇受好评。它将在 12 月 2 日，在京都祗园开设第二家分店。店内的选书工作，交由恵文社一乗寺店负责。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101509zZfUtLON6AMhXY9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101509KyeUNnatmC9g6Hhv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101508d9w3Xj14I2ZoOzQl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101508iE2wuncGZQAzyYC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281015207bBjROAXL0pGzTsx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101520S7tO3Kr4ukwxPBEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/digger-2016-autumn-issue\" rel=\"nofollow\">球鞋杂志《Digger》发布 2016 秋季号</a>。该刊以 Stephen Curry 的白描肖像做封面，挖掘了 Curry 的成长之路上的点滴。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281015352sKZg45heTEU1azu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101552fCwRix7L0bJ6B3yt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101553034PB6RsLCDy2Que.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101553iyhNCGJtuHkISwBf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101601cfXZNrK4VGoblaYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281016088uxpBEswzQ1c4KYG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/gucci-2016-tiger-print-espadrille\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 发布全新的  Tiger Espadrilles 帆布便鞋</a>，这双鞋在帆布鞋面上有着 Gucci 的老虎印花，还保留了编织侧边和生胶鞋底的经典细节。这双鞋现在已由 Mr Porter 发售，售价为 296.47 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101429zV4fTPGXIo7sn3tu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611281014295J62zqi9VuP1oLYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101438s2tlao0FcI5Zn1W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101438a24qQjR71K0P3Xob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101445cQyfBUPb89S7oJZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/27/visvim-dotera-down-jacket/\" rel=\"nofollow\">visvim 发布今年的秋冬新作  DOTERA DOWN COAT</a>，灵感来自日本的传统和服。这件外套共有黑、红、蓝三色，定价为 198000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101400M2A3zfLsZ0wWFplQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101409mkLvcgFVOCDBIxUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016112810140942acGs0myXh3zMWp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161128101418qf4OK9hDaWMzZcS1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}